products.name: Apple Wireless Keyboard
products.description:
• Apple wireless keyboard with built-in Bluetooth has 30-ft. range
  • Compact design takes up 24% less space on your desktop than full-size keyboard

  • Intelligent power management system conserves battery life
  • Uses 2 AA batteries

products.description:

  • Miniature sensors detect even the slightest movement
  • Bluetooth wireless technology
  • Touch sensitive

products.name: Apple TV 1080p Streaming Player
products.description:
This compact Apple TV 1080p streaming player with built-in Wi-Fi lets you play subscription content from iTunes, Netflix, Hulu Plus, YouTube and your favorite sports leagues on your HDTV.  It also streams music, videos, movies and photos from your Mac, PC and Apple devices.

  • Easily connects to your HDTV and Wi-Fi network (compatible with most HDTVs); also has 10/100 Base-T Ethernet port for wired connection to internet
  • Enjoy viewing in vibrant Full HD (1080p) resolution
  • AirPlay lets you wirelessly stream content from your iPhone, iPad and iPod touch to your HDTV – it can even mirror exactly what’s on your display to the big screen
  • iCloud stores your photos and pushes them wirelessly to all your compatible devices
  • Powered by Apple A5 processor
  • Great connectivity options with HDMI port (cable not included), IR receiver, micro USB port, Ethernet and optical audio
  • Includes power cord and Apple Remote
  • Approx. 4"W x 4"D x 1"H
  • Limited warranty

products.name: Apple iPod Nano - 16GB
products.description:
• Apple iPod nano with anodized aluminum design is ultraportable and just plain fun
  • About the size of a credit card, it lets you enjoy your favorite music, FM radio, photos and videos anywhere
  • With its easy-to-use controls, you can give the iPod nano a shake to shuffle to a different song in your music library, tap Genius to find songs that go great together, tap LivePause to pause FM radio without missing a minute, and more
  • 2.5" widescreen multi-touch display
  • 16GB internal flash memory
  • Bluetooth 4.0
  • Built-in pedometer and Nike+ support for fitness
  • USB 2.0 port
  • Headphone jack
  • Rechargeable lithium-ion battery provides up to 30 hours of audio playback or 3.5 hours of video playback on a single charge
  • Includes Apple EarPods headphones and Lightning to USB cable
  • Approx. 1-1/2"W x 1/5"D x 3"H; weighs 1.1 oz.

products.name: Apple iPad mini 16GB WiFi White
products.description:
Get everything you love in the iPad in a smaller package! This premium quality Apple iPad mini features a vivid 7.9" multi-touch display, FaceTime HD and iSight cameras, ultrafast dual-band Wi-Fi, Bluetooth 4.0 wireless technology, and up to 10 hours of battery life. It lets you easily download content, stream video and browse the web at amazing speeds. You also have access to more than 275,00 popular apps at the App Store.

  • 512MB system memory
  • 5 megapixel iSight camera with advanced optics and face detection for great shots every time plus Full HD (1080p) video recording
  • Comes with rechargeable lithium-polymer battery (up to 10 hours of battery life on a single charge), lightning to USB cable and USB power adapter

products.name: Apple iPhone 6 16GB Unlocked Smartphone
products.description:
Unlocked cell phones are compatible with GSM networks like AT&T and T-Mobile in the U.S. or any GSM network around the world. Phone will not work with Sprint, Verizon, Boost Mobile, Virgin Wireless or any other CDMA network.

 

If you are purchasing this device for use on a GSM network like T-Mobile or AT&T, please contact your carrier prior to purchasing to confirm your carrier will support voice and data on this unlocked GSM device.

 

Please read and fully understand this unlocked device prior to purchase.

 

Apple iPhone 6 Unlocked Smartphone
Thin iPhone 6 with large Retina HD touch screen lets you talk, text, surf the web and stay connected to emails and your favorite social network sites. Built-in 3x faster Wi-Fi lets you connect to the internet without using your data plan. Includes built-in Bluetooth LE, AirPlay Mirroring, MP3 playback, speakerphone, customizable ring tones and voice mail.

  • 4.7" Retina capacitive multi-touch screen with HD (720p) resolution
  • Powered by Apple iOS 8 operating system and A8 chipset
  • 16GB internal memory
  • 8MP iSight camera with phase detection auto focus, exposure control and True Tone flash plus FaceTime HD camera

 

Model#: Apple iPhone 6
GSM bands: 850/900/1800/1900
HSDPA bands: 850/900/1700/1900/2100
LTE bands: 700/800/850/900/1800/1900/2100/2600

Your carrier will need the info above to confirm if the phone is supported on its network.

 

RETURNS ARE LIMITED FOR MOBILE DEVICES
Once shipped, only defective and damaged devices can be exchanged for an identical device on phones. Defective and damaged exchanges must be within 30 days of purchase.

 

NOTE: Unlocked phones may arrive unsealed and the phone may appear previously handled. The unlocking procedure may have required a technician to unseal the box and manually handle the cell phone to restore it to default settings – the cell phone should not be considered “tampered with” or “defective.” All warranties offered by us or our partners are still valid.
